# .gitignore for PHIght Club (.NET / Visual Studio)

## Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
*/bin/
*/obj/

## Rider
.idea/

## Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## VS Code
.vscode/

## Logs
logs/
*.log

## Publish output
publish/
artifacts/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
.nuget/
packages/

## Test results
TestResults/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## OS generated
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ignore build outputs created during local runs
src/**/bin/
src/**/obj/
tests/**/bin/
tests/**/obj/

# Ignore local configuration
local.settings.json

